<div id="review_397451220" class="review nosyndicate" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/397451220" />
    <a title="Terri" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/1968826-terri"><img alt="Terri" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1356560426p2/1968826.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/397451220?book_show_action=true">Aug 21, 2012</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Terri" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Terri" href="/user/show/1968826-terri">Terri</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was ok"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was ok</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Paperback 9780765303721" href="/book/show/2399668.The_Skystone">review of another edition</a>


        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/1968826-terri?shelf=historical-fiction">historical-fiction</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/1968826-terri?shelf=britain-fiction">britain-fiction</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer397451220" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer7100771115893898096">I always try and say something semi constructive in a review, but there really isn&apos;t anything I can say that hasn&apos;t already been said by fellow Goodreads member, Tasha (who read Skystone at the same time as me).<br/>So, I am going to take the cop out option and direct you there as I echo her sentiments... <a target='_blank' rel='noopener nofollow' href='https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/431987795'>http://www.goodreads.com/review/show/...</a>... and if you do not want to read her review, then here you go.<br/>The sex and the timing of the sex was a big joke, the flow was uninspiring, the writing for me</span>
  <span id="freeText7100771115893898096" style="display:none">I always try and say something semi constructive in a review, but there really isn't anything I can say that hasn't already been said by fellow Goodreads member, Tasha (who read Skystone at the same time as me).<br />So, I am going to take the cop out option and direct you there as I echo her sentiments... <a target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/431987795">http://www.goodreads.com/review/show/...</a>... and if you do not want to read her review, then here you go.<br />The sex and the timing of the sex was a big joke, the flow was uninspiring, the writing for me was a trial and tribulation. I gave up on this book just passed halfway.</span>
  <a data-text-id="7100771115893898096" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


      <div class="reviewFooter uitext buttons">
          

