        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer913286027" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer8723704258149197661">I&apos;ve always been a fan of historical fiction. Authors like Wilbur Smith entertain while providing a historical narrative. Jack Whyte is really good at this craft. I read his William Wallace, Robert the Bruce series which was excellent. This book tells the story of the end of the Roman rule in Britain.<br/><br/>It is told quickly, yet descriptively. A great read and for people that enjoy historic fiction, fantastic!</span>
  <span id="freeText8723704258149197661" style="display:none">I've always been a fan of historical fiction. Authors like Wilbur Smith entertain while providing a historical narrative. Jack Whyte is really good at this craft. I read his William Wallace, Robert the Bruce series which was excellent. This book tells the story of the end of the Roman rule in Britain.<br /><br />It is told quickly, yet descriptively. A great read and for people that enjoy historic fiction, fantastic!</span>
