<div id="review_1464919836" class="review nosyndicate" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/1464919836" />
    <a title="Hassan" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/46287846-hassan"><img alt="Hassan" src="https://s.gr-assets.com/assets/nophoto/user/m_50x66-82093808bca726cb3249a493fbd3bd0f.png" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/1464919836?book_show_action=true">Dec 09, 2015</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Hassan" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Hassan" href="/user/show/46287846-hassan">Hassan</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Mass Market Paperback 9780140170504" href="/book/show/1374842.The_Skystone">review of another edition</a>


        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/46287846-hassan?shelf=own">own</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1464919836" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer8790719766452619368">If you&apos;re not paying attention, this book reads as just another possible chapter in the history of Roman Britain. If you read closely though, you can see hints of the Arthurian legend in the shadows, waiting and growing, biding its time, until it is called forth to center stage. A wonderful read.</span>
  <span id="freeText8790719766452619368" style="display:none">If you're not paying attention, this book reads as just another possible chapter in the history of Roman Britain. If you read closely though, you can see hints of the Arthurian legend in the shadows, waiting and growing, biding its time, until it is called forth to center stage. A wonderful read.</span>
  <a data-text-id="8790719766452619368" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
